interpretation: The "tractor" card represents hard work and determination. It signifies the need to roll up your sleeves and get to work, even if it means getting your hands dirty. This card reminds you that success doesn't come easily, and that you must be willing to put in the effort if you want to achieve your goals. The tractor also represents progress and forward movement. It suggests that you are on the right path, and that you are moving steadily towards your destination. However, be careful not to get too caught up in your work, as this card can also indicate a need to take a break and recharge. Remember to balance your hard work with rest and relaxation to avoid burnout. Overall, the "tractor" card is a symbol of persistence, productivity, and the rewards that come from diligent effort.
